{"tid":370990,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"係外國碌信用卡","createTime":"2017-08-23T11:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T16:00:31.000Z","uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a80d026aa2cb5e28c021cd893e5e89c8d3d3d1","tid":370990,"uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"下個月終於第一次衝出亞洲<br />\n<br />\n去得歐洲多數就拎信用卡黎碌<br />\n<br />\n所以最近先開始研究下D信用卡<br />\n<br />\n咁話說小弟將會去波蘭<br />\n<br />\n諗住網上買波蘭國鐵既車飛個陣見台仔話一定要有3D 驗證<br />\n<br />\n後來睇返先知係銀行會SEND 個SMS黎俾我<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦, 去到外國, 收撚鬼到SMS咩, 就算收到每次碌咪都要收錢?<br />\n<br />\n然後再睇返我申請個張星展信用卡, 好似一申請已經有3D驗證依樣野<br />\n<br />\n我想問我有無理解錯3D 驗證, 同埋應該點算? <br />\n<br />\n唔該晒"},{"pid":"70d404e6249dc74df52e64a39d2204fd735dae94","tid":370990,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:11:12.000Z","msg":"車飛係香港買定咪得"},{"pid":"d4c5b0bd8876178a0bdb234615ac4431e08d48fa","tid":370990,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>車飛係香港買定咪得</blockquote><br />\n同埋係鋪頭買野唔會要你入sms code<br />\n最多叫你入pin code"},{"pid":"e4ba53da744f2f2ecd0d69fe9bd927e7ae919452","tid":370990,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>車飛係香港買定咪得</blockquote><br />\n同埋係鋪頭買野唔會要你入sms code<br />\n最多叫你入pin code</blockquote><br />\n我上次都係上網買定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到買排死你 啲人做野勁慢"},{"pid":"34665b86a16c7ee5cd7bd8abf51bba8699d706c8","tid":370990,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"收 SMS  係唔收錢，但用漫遊就要小心有電話入同部電話會唔會偷偷上網拎 Data , 果啲先金。<br />\n<br />\n用開 HSBC 用密碼認証，有時上咗車先再上網買飛。"},{"pid":"656ad8afc82e03d7bc22cbba83fdbeff4c5bf206","tid":370990,"uid":82641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"打上去話要境外收sms 但唔要data<br />\n電話公司會幫你set<br />\n<br />\n如果你去到外地 網上買野 先要sms<br />\n收sms 唔洗錢<br />\n<br />\nLook 真卡 個陣 唔會要sms<br />\n有可能會問你有冇pin<br />\n你話無就得"},{"pid":"5e8dc9cc90f5d964f58a31b1e9c72c2106d93c01","tid":370990,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"去鴨記買張ABC mobile最平嗰張<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcsl.com/tc/abc-Mobile-Local-Prepaid-SIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcsl.com%2Ftc%2Fabc-Mobile-Local-Prepaid-SIM%2F&d=ox5U%2F7G%2FhUOIrXJuGdZiwC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ba476019\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcsl.com/tc/abc-Mobile-Local-Prepaid-SIM/</a><br />\n呢張卡冇開plan用唔到數據<br />\n<br />\n再將收SMS嗰電話轉落去呢張"},{"pid":"706619d7520f400137b248f282eec6cdc3b72c1e","tid":370990,"uid":82641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去鴨記買張ABC mobile最平嗰張<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcsl.com/tc/abc-Mobile-Local-Prepaid-SIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcsl.com%2Ftc%2Fabc-Mobile-Local-Prepaid-SIM%2F&d=ox5U%2F7G%2FhUOIrXJuGdZiwC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ba476019\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcsl.com/tc/abc-Mobile-Local-Prepaid-SIM/</a><br />\n呢張卡冇開plan用唔到數據<br />\n<br />\n再將收SMS嗰電話轉落去呢張</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗搞咁多丫<br />\n打上電話台就得"},{"pid":"141e67122caa3d3338d8ab181ccb378792c0bd61","tid":370990,"uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"好唔該晒咁多位巴絲打<br />\n<br />\n我諗碌真卡個陣係唔需要sms密碼<br />\n<br />\n但我聽日會再打去俾星展confirm多次<br />\n<br />\nbtw...東亞間野好似無3D 驗證(亦都唔見有得申請)...諗住拎張後備卡黎買車飛 頂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c6fe6b4a618d0777cc37fbabfa7d94a1261da6","tid":370990,"uid":129835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"去到外國買飛，佢要輸入密碼，個密碼即係atm 提款個密碼？"},{"pid":"21d8122ffd3c1da9fa47b7401296973f82f2793b","tid":370990,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquo